---
title: Greek-Inspired Sheet Pan Chicken and Veggies with Tomato Orzo and Feta
description: This sheet pan dinner is loaded with bold Greek-inspired flavours and is oh-so-simple to make. After a bit of prep, the oven does most of the work and you'll end up with a feast for the eyes and the taste buds!
